Why Opus



Latest News
Third consecutive year Opus receives Top Guns Award from PSN Informa
How can the addition of a new asset class increase the return while reducing overall risk of your portfolio? What benefits might you realize if you widen your potential universe of investments while remaining within regulatory guidelines? How will changes in your underwriting results affect the level of investment risk you are willing to take? Let us show you.
Asking such questions is where knowledge becomes power – in the open exchange of vital information and the creative application of new ideas. That's where Opus has the answers. At Opus Investment Management, an 
      SEC-registered investment advisor, we strive to realize the power of knowledge in everything we do – from searching for every extra basis point, to empowering our clients to become strong advocates for their portfolios, and to creating investment solutions customized to fit specific operating constraints.
In the following pages, we invite you to learn more about how we apply knowledge–of investments and of insurance–to open a world
      of new possibilities.




