Sheryl W. O'Connell, CFA
Vice President
MS Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute
BS West Virginia Wesleyan College 
Ms. O’Connell joined Opus Investment Management in 2007 and is currently the Head of Structured Product. In this role she oversees the mortgage research group which is responsible for analysis and monitoring of all structured mortgage products, including agency and other residential and commercial mortgage-backed securities, asset-backed securities and direct commercial mortgages. Additionally, she is responsible for the management of several client portfolios.







